entries.femaleVariant: Lookin' at these people, whattaya see?
Uh-huh. I see one secret after another. Each an' every one of 'em's got somethin' to hide.
You find that somethin', you'll own these people. Just like their megacorp.
Then, you don't even gotta ask nice. You just get what you want. Data, tapes, deep, dark corpo secrets.
And THAT'S when the real scratch starts to flow.
